item.title: By: Aarav Shahi
item.dc:creator: Aarav Shahi
item.description: The Winter Frost Knitscarf is a winter essential for me. The white color is timeless, and the quality of the knitting is exceptional. It's my go-to scarf for staying cozy and looking elegant all season long.

item.description: I am absolutely in love with the Winter Frost Knitscarf! The white wool is so soft and luxurious, and it keeps me warm and stylish during the colder months. It's a versatile accessory that adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit.
